TI  - The chemical convulsant diisopropylfluorophosphate (DFP) causes persistent neuropathology in adult male rats independent of seizure activity
AU  - González, Eduardo A.
AU  - Rindy, Alexa C.
AU  - Guignet, Michelle A.
AU  - Calsbeek, Jonas J.
