TI  - Peripheral and central effects of NADPH oxidase inhibitor, mitoapocynin, in a rat model of diisopropylfluorophosphate (DFP) toxicity
AU  - Meyer, Christina
AU  - Rao, Nikhil S.
AU  - Vasanthi, Suraj S.
