TI  - Lacto-N-fucopentaose-III ameliorates acute and persisting hippocampal synaptic plasticity and transmission deficits in a Gulf War Illness mouse model
AU  - Brown, Kyle A.
AU  - Carpenter, Jessica M.
AU  - Preston, Collin J.
AU  - Ludwig, Helaina D.
AU  - Clay, Kendall B.
AU  - Harn, Donald A.
